'From Squeak3.1alpha of 5 February 2001 [latest update: #4336] on 13 September 2001 at 7:24:34 pm'!"Change Set:		ClipTextSelectionDate:			13 September 2001Author:			Dan IngallsNed Konz reported text selections displaying outside the bounds of a textMorph.This fixes the problem."!!FormCanvas methodsFor: 'drawing' stamp: 'di 9/12/2001 21:38'!paragraph: para bounds: bounds color: c	| scanner |	self setPaintColor: c.	scanner _ (port clippedBy: (bounds translateBy: origin)) displayScannerFor: para		foreground: (self shadowColor ifNil:[c]) background: Color transparent		ignoreColorChanges: self shadowColor notNil.	para displayOn: (self copyClipRect: bounds) using: scanner at: origin+ bounds topLeft.! !